an Rawling \u2013 production\n*[[Brian Higgins (producer)|Brian Higgins]] \u2013 composition\n*Stuart McLennen \u2013 composition\n*[[Paul Barry (songwriter)|Paul Barry]] \u2013 composition\n*Steven Torch \u2013 composition\n*Matthew Gray \u2013 composition\n{{col-2}}\n*[[Tim Powell (producer)|Timothy Powell]] \u2013 composition\n*Gypsyland \u2013 background vocals, guitar\n*Robin Smith \u2013 arranger\n*Adam Phillips \u2013 additional guitars\n*Ryan Art \u2013 designer\n*Michael Lavine \u2013 cover art photographer\n*[[Rob Dickins]] \u2013 executive production\n{{col-end}}\nCredits adapted from ''Believe'' album liner notes.\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Chart (1998\u20131999)\n!Peak<br>position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|1|artist=Cher|song=Believe|accessdate=October 31, 2015}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|2|artist=Cher|song=Believe|accessdate=October 31, 2015}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders|1|artist=Cher|song=Believe|accessdate=October 31, 2015}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia|1|artist=Cher|song=Believe|accessdate=October 31, 2015}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Belgium (Promuvi)<ref name=\"belg\">{{cite web |url=http://www.americanradiohistory.com/Archive-Billboard/90s/1998/BB-1998-12-19.pdf |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20150428043655/http://www.americanradiohistory.com/Archive-Billboard/90s/1998/BB-1998-12-19.pdf |url-status=dead |archive-date=2015-04-28 |title=Hits of the World |work=Billboard |accessdate=October 31, 2015 }}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|-\n{{singlechart|Canadatopsingles|1|chartid=7494|accessdate=October 31, 2015}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Canadaadultcontemporary|1|chartid=7140|accessdate=October 31, 2015}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Canadadance|1|chartid=7486|accessdate=February 6, 2020}}\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Canada ([[Canadian Singles Chart]])<ref name=\"allmusic\">{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/cher-mn0000107090/awards|title=Cher Awards|publisher=[[AllMusic]]|accessdate=